    <string name="disclaimer_title">User Agreement &amp; Privacy Statement</string>
    <string name="disclaimer_text">Please read the following terms carefully before using this app. By using this app, you acknowledge that you have read and agree to all terms.\n\nI. Non-official Identity Statement\nThis app is a third-party schedule tool independently developed by a student. It has no affiliation, authorization, cooperation, or association with Guangdong University of Science and Technology. References to the school\'s name and logos are for functional display purposes only and do not represent the school\'s official position. The school assumes no responsibility for any content or services provided by this app.\n\nII. Data Accuracy Disclaimer\n1. Academic data such as courses and exams are obtained through the school\'s unified authentication system. This app only organizes and displays this data and makes no guarantees regarding its authenticity, accuracy, completeness, or timeliness.\n2. All teaching arrangements, classroom changes, and exam information should be verified through the school\'s official mini-program, DingTalk notifications, or academic system. The developer assumes no responsibility for any losses resulting from data delays, discrepancies, or omissions.\n\nIII. Account &amp; Privacy Protection\n1. Campus account credentials are only used to log in to the school\'s official authentication system to retrieve academic data. All account information is encrypted and stored locally on your device only and will never be uploaded to any third-party servers. The developer cannot access or retain your account information.\n2. Please keep your campus account secure. You are solely responsible for any consequences resulting from account leaks or improper account management.\n\nIV. Usage Guidelines\n1. This app is for personal, non-commercial, educational use only. Commercial use, repackaging, redistribution, reverse engineering, or content tampering is prohibited.\n2. Please use this app responsibly and avoid making excessive high-frequency requests to the school\'s system interfaces. Users are solely responsible for any impact on the school\'s servers caused by abuse.\n\nV. Limitation of Liability\n1. The developer does not guarantee that this app will be permanently available and reserves the right to update, suspend, or terminate services at any time without prior notice.\n2. To the maximum extent permitted by law, the developer assumes no liability for any direct or indirect losses arising from the use or inability to use this app.\n\nVI. Other\nThe developer reserves the final right to interpret this agreement. Any updates to these terms will be announced within the app. Continued use constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.\nIf you do not agree to any of the above terms, please stop using this app immediately.</string>
    <string name="disclaimer_text_short">This app is a third-party schedule tool developed by a student, with no official affiliation with Guangdong University of Science and Technology.\nCourse data is sourced from the school\'s academic system for display purposes only; accuracy is not guaranteed. Please refer to official channels for information.\nAccount credentials are encrypted and stored locally, never uploaded to any third-party servers.\nAll risks and consequences arising from the use of this app are borne by the user.</string>
